The paper deals with interactive exploration of large multimedia collections using visual and textual content. This involves learning on the fly new analytic categories and working with limited computing resources. These topics are closely related to information retrieval (cs.IR), computer vision (cs.CV), multimedia (cs.MM), natural language processing (cs.CL), and deep learning (cs.DL). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
